edu.biu.scapi.primitives.prf
Interface TripleDES

All Superinterfaces:
PrfFixed, PrpFixed, PseudorandomFunction, PseudorandomPermutation
All Known Implementing Classes:
BcTripleDES, OpenSSLTripleDES
public interface TripleDES
extends PrpFixed

Marker interface. Every class that implements it is signed as TripleDes. TripleDes is a blockCipher with fixed input and output lengths and thus implements the interface PrpFixed.

Author:
Cryptography and Computer Security Research Group Department of Computer Science Bar-Ilan University (Meital Levy)
